"Decorator to ensure a database connection is active.\n"
"\n"
"    Example:\n"
"    ```python\n"
"    @ensure_db_connection()\n"
"    @commands.command()\n"
"    async def mycommand(self, ctx):\n"
"        await ctx.send(\"Database connection is active\")\n"
"    ```\n"
